title: Metal Fingers (MF DOOM) Special Herbs: The Box Set Vol. 0&ndash;
description:
This limited edition box set of Metal Fingers' Special Herbs is made up of 3 CD's. The first two, are mixed extracts from the initial ten volumes of the Special Herbs series. The third disc is a collection of KMD instrumentals. The Box Set was released on January 24, 2006, limited to 7,500 copies.

Released	January 24, 2006
Genre	Underground hip hop
Length	4 hr, 28 min, 20 sec
Label	Nature Sounds
Producer	Metal Fingers, DJ Subroc

Imported from iTunes in m4a format, complete with correct track listing and artwork.
